author: @SamuelM.-iz1un
content: @@louiselouisethebest Mariah doesn’t sing like she use to. Her live concerts are part live and other parts pre-recorded. High note range parts are pre-recorded. When a woman singer starts entering menopause, most start losing their range and sound hoarse.
